```

**예상 구조** (가이드 문서 기반):
```kotlin
// user-module/src/main/kotlin/com/maum/backend/service/UserService.kt

@Service
@Transactional
class UserService(
    private val userRepository: UserRepository,
    private val redisTemplate: RedisTemplate<String, Any>,
